NUMBER 2540
NAME Ruined World, ledge
REGION 12
CHANNEL 84
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
DAY_LIGHT
MONSTER_GROUP 92
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Fantastic purple, gold, and red colors fill the sky above this wind-swept
ledge. Crumbled stairs lead down to a shattered landscape filled with ruined
buildings. Glowing red craters dot the ground and generate nearly overwhelming
waves of heat. A dry, sickly wind blows incessantly across the broken ground,
producing a mournful wailing sound as it passes through the ruined hulks. Red
sand has piled up against an exit, and the wind swirls it into the darkness
beyond. There is also a shimmering gate hovering here.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT O 2541
EXIT D 2555
ITEM 2 763 ADJ1=287 VAL2=2096
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
The doors are very aged, but you can see the faint impression of what seems to be a large eagle holding a flaming sword in its talons, the eagle is surrounded by five golden crowns in a circle around it.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
Peering closer at the stairway you notice that there has been some recent work done to it. The stairway seems a lot sturdier now, almost as if someone has prepared it for your coming...
*DESCRIPTION_END
;
