A wide hallway runs north through a sand filled exit leading outside to a section of wall that is blue in color. Next to the metallic blue wall is a panel with the imprint of a hand on it. A fine red sand swirls throughout the corridor, borne in from the outside by the howling wind that seems ever present upon this strange world. Light fills the corridor, cast by strange round balls of glass set at intervals into the walls.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT N 2540
ITEM 1 282
ITEM 2 420 ADJ1=192 ADJ2=29
