NUMBER 2555
NAME Complex, stairway
REGION 12
CHANNEL 84
DAY_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_OTHER
MONSTER_GROUP 92
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
A small platform marks the center of this long stairway. Above the platform,
the companionway ascends higher into the mountains, while below the platform
it descends to a large open flat area. From this viewpoint one can discern
more details about this strange world. Spanning the western horizon is a long
canyon. This abyss, like a deep wound in the earth, bleeds titanic gouts of
flame that spiral high into the air before coming crashing down into its
depths once again. Far to the southwest stand the ruined husks of tall
buildings that once made up a large settlement. To the north and northwest
stretches an endless cratered wasteland reeking with sickness and disease.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT U 2540
EXIT D 2556
;
NUMBER 2556
NAME Complex, open lot
REGION 12
CHANNEL 84
DAY_LIGHT
MONSTER_GROUP 92
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
A tall wire fence surrounds a square open lot. Hard black stone covers its
surface. The ground is cracked and pitted in many places, but one can still
make out many areas where yellow lines were painted on the surface. Strewn
about the lot are the rotting remains of squarish metal boxes. The boxes are
fairly large, big enough to comfortably hold humanoids it seems, though their
present rotted condition keeps anyone from entering. Set into the center of
the fence to the west is a large gate. Next to the gate is a small wooden
house that creaks and sways precariously in the hot wind that blows off
the wastelands. The door to the small house lies on the ground in front
of it, allowing easy entrance through an opening. At the eastern end of
the lot a stone stairway winds its way up the mountain.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT U 2555
ITEM 1 72 VAL2=2557
ITEM 2 68 VAL1=500 VAL2=2558 VAL3=45
IFENTRY
	IFITEM 2 OPEN
		ECHO PLAYER The gate is open.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFTOUCH 2
        IFITEM 2 CLOSED
		EQUAL ROUNDTIME 5
		ECHO PLAYER A jolt of electricity runs through you as you touch the gate.%c [round: 5 sec]
		ECHO OTHERS A jolt of blue electricity runs through %N when %s touches the gate!
		DAMAGE ELECTRIC 30 %N is thrown away from the gate by powerful electricity!
	ENDIF
ENDIF
