NUMBER 2557
NAME Complex, small house
REGION 12
CHANNEL 84
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
INDOOR_FLOOR
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
A faintly glowing red dust covers the inside of this small house. More the
size of a small room, the shelter contains little as furnishings. A small table
and a chair sit in one corner. A small box made of some unknown material sits
on top of the table. The box seemed to have a small window of some kind set
into one side, but this window has long been shattered exposing a strange
conglomeration of wires and little green boards inside the box. The red
dust swirls as you wander throughout the room, rising to your face and
making you feel slightly nauseous.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT O 2556
ITEM 1 247 ADJ1=25
IFVERB SEARCH -1
	RANDOM DUMMY1 1 100 0
	ADD DUMMY1 PER
	IFVAR DUMMY1 > 160
		ECHO PLAYER You spot a small black button underneath the table!
		ECHO OTHERS %N found something!
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB PUSH 1
  ECHO ALL You hear a loud grinding noise outside.
  AFFECT 2556
  IFITEM 2 CLOSED
    EQUAL BRECKA 1
  	ECHO ALL The gate slides apart with a ponderous noise.
  	OPEN 2
    AFFECT 2558
    ECHO ALL The gate slides apart with a ponderous noise.
    OPEN 2
    AFFECT 2556
  ENDIF
  AFFECT 2556
  IFITEM 2 OPEN
    IFVAR BRECKA = 0
      ECHO ALL The gate slides shut with a ponderous noise.
      CLOSE 2
      AFFECT 2558
      ECHO ALL The gate slides shut with a ponderous noise.
      CLOSE 2
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
  EQUAL BRECKA 0
ENDIF
