ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
This section of the village is filled with healthy growing natural things.
Vibrant trees with colorful leaves, lush bushes filled with ripe, delicious
fruits, and plots of ground in which healthy looking vegetables grow
vibrantly, all combine to form a beautiful garden that represents nature
at its most wonderful. A clear, sparkling stream runs through the flower
beds, adding its own vibrancy to this swatch of paradise. The whole area
fills the senses with delicious feelings of robust healthy power. Yet at
the edges of the garden, one can see that this wonderful place is slowly
dying, despite the best efforts of its tenders. Dying foliage and drooping
plants signal that the ravages of outside world are slowly bringing an end
to what is possibly one of the most beautiful spots in many worlds.
*DESCRIPTION_END
