NUMBER 2567
NAME Wasteland
REGION 12
CHANNEL 84
DAY_LIGHT
WASTE
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
The wastes come to an end at this point, continuing south and northwest. You
stand on the eastern edge and peer out across the plateau covered with large
and small craters. Far off, on the horizon, the hazy outline of mountains
can be seen. The wide open plain the spreads out before you seems difficult
to cross, yet someone has done so, evidenced by the sandy slope which leads
to a faint path through the crater field.
*DESCRIPTION_END
MONSTER_GROUP 93
ITEM 1 611 ADJ1=274 VAL2=1475 ; Slope to 1475
EXIT S 2569
EXIT NW 2566
IFPREVERB CLIMB 1
  ECHO PLAYER You carefully wind your way down the slope.
  ECHO OTHERS %N carefully climbs down the slope.
  EQUAL ROUNDTIME 8
ENDIF
IFENTRY
   RANDOM DUMMY1 1 10 0
   PLREVENT 2
   CONTPLREVENT
   IFVAR DUMMY1 > 7
     ECHO ALL A shrill keening wail resonates from the east. Turning in that direction you see a desert jackal slowly sinking into quicksand.
   ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVAR INTNUM87 = 0
     RANDOM DUMMY1 1 100 0
     IFVAR DUMMY1 > 90
        RANDOM DUMMY1 1 100 0
        ADD DUMMY1 CON
        IFVAR DUMMY1 < 170
           IFVAR DEAD = 0
             IFVAR RAC < 7
              DAMAGE DISEASE 6 The infectious atmosphere gets into your blood.%c>
             ENDIF
            ENDIF
        ENDIF
     ENDIF
ENDIF
