NUMBER 1475
NAME Wasteland, edge of the plateau
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
You step out onto the hard packed plateau and feel the heat rising out of
the ground. The ground smoothes out before you becoming a flat plain that
spreads to the horizon. Craters of every size fill the landscape. Once the
craters, almost on top of each other, had high walls making passage an
impossibility. Now, due to the endless erosion affects of the wind,
the pockmarked landscape has been reduced to passable rolling peaks and
valleys.
*DESCRIPTION_END
